#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.rename.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.rename"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.series_rename:1 of
msgid "Alter Series index labels or name."
msgstr "修改 Series 索引标签或名称。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.series_rename:3 of
msgid ""
"Function / dict values must be unique (1-to-1). Labels not contained in a"
" dict / Series will be left as-is. Extra labels listed don't throw an "
"error."
msgstr ""
"函数或字典的值必须是一一对应的。不在字典或 Series 中的标签将保持原样不变"
"。列出的多余标签不会引发错误。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.series_rename:7 of
msgid "Alternatively, change ``Series.name`` with a scalar value."
msgstr "或者，使用标量值更改 ``Series.name``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.series_rename of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.series_rename:9 of
msgid "Unused. Accepted for compatibility with DataFrame method only."
msgstr "未使用。仅为了与 DataFrame 方法兼容而接受。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.series_rename:11 of
msgid ""
"Functions or dict-like are transformations to apply to the index. Scalar "
"or hashable sequence-like will alter the ``Series.name`` attribute."
msgstr ""
"函数或类字典对象是应用于索引的变换。标量或可哈希的序列类对象将更改 ``"
"Series.name`` 属性。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.series_rename:16 of
msgid ""
"Additional keyword arguments passed to the function. Only the \"inplace\""
" keyword is used."
msgstr "传递给函数的额外关键字参数。仅使用 \"inplace\" 关键字。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.series_rename of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.series_rename:19 of
msgid "Series with index labels or name altered."
msgstr "索引标签或名称被更改的 Series。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.series_rename of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.series_rename:24 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.rename`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.series_rename:25 of
msgid "Corresponding DataFrame method."
msgstr "对应的 DataFrame 方法。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.series_rename:27 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.rename_axis`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.series_rename:28 of
msgid "Set the name of the axis."
msgstr "设置轴的名称。"

